commit 68c45e66bc580c485aab1309d7b9ff84fcd5ef91
Author: Greg Rundlett <greg.rundlett@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Aug 22 10:45:23 2025 -0400

    Default to ansible_env.USER for ansible_user
    
    When all plays are executed by the 'Application User' (meza-ansible)
    then the ansible environment will know the USER as 'meza-ansible'
    
    This works even in instances when ansible.cfg is not read in.
    
    relevant to Issue #186

