Date:   Tue Aug 5 21:15:17 2025 -0400

    Update README with component logos

commit bb2f80c1488c50188f0318bc066a4ee893a8c4d6
Author: Greg Rundlett <greg.rundlett@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Aug 5 14:45:49 2025 -0400

    Update CHANGELOG for REL1_43

commit 2be7babd70e896307b9f937cc1960ea0bf5046d1
Merge: 131c9c20 ac1eb9c5
Author: Greg Rundlett <greg.rundlett@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Aug 5 06:40:36 2025 -0400

    Merge branch 'feature/sbom' into REL1_43
    
    Script to regularly generate a Software Bill Of Materials (SBOM)
    
    The generated SBOMs will include all 200+ packages
    from your MediaWiki ecosystem, properly categorized
    by scope and type, with complete license and metadata information.
    
    - Parse your composer.lock + composer.local.lock to extract all dependencies
    - Generate industry-standard SBOM formats (SPDX, CycloneDX)
    - Provide human-readable summaries
    - Automatically update when dependencies change
    - Support security and compliance requirements
    - Integrate with CI/CD pipelines
    
    @see docs at https://github.com/freephile/meza/blob/REL1_43/src/scripts/sbom.md

commit 131c9c205cb4170cb22b6e8fb41ac2d2b44325e4
Merge: 3588683f 4f3323fe
Author: Greg Rundlett <greg.rundlett@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Aug 5 06:31:24 2025 -0400

    Merge branch 'main' into REL1_43
    
    Add script to show git (annotated) tags
    @see https://github.com/freephile/meza/blob/4f3323fe8c1eccc006b170b5d7c98a76b5f9fe9f/src/scripts/showTags.md

