commit 816854ade748f91cdc352c14470676d6d7902b7e
Author: James Montalvo <edwin.j.montalvo@nasa.gov>
Date:   Fri Sep 20 16:35:09 2024 -0500

    fix(vuln): remove default elasticsearch password
    
    Setting a default password could cause installations to use that
    password in production systems, which is a security vulnerability since
    the default password is published on github.

